{
  "stem": "10699.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They just gave you a, a, a, a, a dress from here or skirt from here, a shoe from here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had one shoe with a heel, one without a heel, a little dress, a green dress, I remember, with a little, white collar-- and completely dehumanized in a matter of a few hours.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went out into the open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I could only see two ears, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did-- we-- the girls I saw before and after, I didn't recognize them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know if they-- who was it, you know-- and completely disturbed, completely dehumanized.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had taken everything away from us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In, in no time, we were not anymore the same person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we kept on crying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't help very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they, they, they made us walk into a barrack, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how many we were-- several hundred.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We get into these-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not beds, the--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--bunks, wooden bunks, with one blanket for four or five or six, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were so dejected, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the next thing we knew, we, we asked questions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We tried to get an answer from the so-called other inmates, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I only knew that the next day, when we were on the-- on the Appell, on the call-- 'roll call,' they call it, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] right away, the beatings started, you know, people who couldn't stand, who were too tired-- tired, or who were not behaving according to what the, the system there.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were-- the only thing we were given, really, was-- in a-- in a-- a, a tin container, there was some kind of water with something in it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But, you see, it had to pass from the-- from the beginning to the end.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So if you were in the middle, if-- whatever they add, you got one sip or two.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was your lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Whatever it was-- it was just water for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only thing I remember quite, quite clearly was some people [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] did get in with their mothers, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I saw-- when the mother couldn't stand the appel for so many hours, when they collapsed and the kapo went and started to beat them up, I said, would I have been able to take that, that a kapo or a guard, a German guard, should go and beat my mother up, and I can't do anything about it?",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How would I be able to take that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we were sent right away the next day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think I was in a terrible state because I think I wasn't normal for a few days.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a shock.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I was under-- in shock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they were sent-- we were sent to-- near the railways to make trenches.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we saw arriving the ghetto from Litzmannstadt, the Lodz ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And these people, you could see that they had gone through hell already.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were already skin, skin and bones, badly dressed, in a terrible way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I asked them where they were coming from.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They said they hadn't noticed that we were working there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I asked them where they're coming from.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they told us they came from Litzmannstadt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Nobody came in of these people, nobody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They just passed us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody was allowed into the camp, of that convoy anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Crematorium.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, what we noticed very soon, we were-- we were doing trenches and trenches and trenches.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we, we didn't know why we were doing these trenches, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we soon understood because we were somehow-- our block was facing the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we saw fire-- and the smell, and the-- the terrible smell in the camp, and the flames.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But also sometimes we saw flames coming from the trenches, you see, further along, in the open.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We didn't want to believe all that, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't understand what was happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We kept asking questions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And you could-- and the people that were there already a long time were very hard with us, though.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're so-- they, they made us understand that's how we will finish off, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't mince their words.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I soon-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] on the 17th of August, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was a very big selection.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And on-- I must tell you one thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
